    </dd>
  
</dl></div>

  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>I don't really have a good sense of this. It's easy to project one's own views, or those of people one associates with, on the general public. Those of my friends and I who would vote for a Democrat would likely do so regardless, and the larger number of people I know who are Republican would vote that way regardless. I don't have a good feel for how those who don't typically vote or who are swing voters respond to all of this.</p>

  </div>
  <div class="cf">
  
  <p class="sig">
