    </dd>
  
</dl></div>

  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>and workers wages need to be increased. &nbsp;</p>
<p>If more workers were participating in the workforce with increased wages, there would be more money for the items you mentioned, and less panic (even if it is unnecessarily stirred up by repubs and dems) over solvency and the social safety net.</p>
<p>You're starting at the wrong end, and dems who run on OMG!! the repubs are cutting stuff!! are at the wrong end also.</p>

