<p>Nonfarm employment as measured by the Bureau of Labor Statistics each month:</p>
<p>• January 2009: 133,977,000</p>
<p>• February 2010: 129,649,000 (The lowest point of the Great Recession)</p>
<p>• January 2015: 140,849,000&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</p>

