<li id="c34">

  <div class="cx" id="cx55613244">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">Here's the GOP populist message</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1363137/55613244#c34?mode=alone;showrate=1#c34">21+ / 0-</a>)</span>
  </h5>

  
  


<div class="crs"><dl>
  <dt>Recommended by:</dt><dd>
  <a href="/user/uid:31900">pat bunny</a>, <a href="/user/uid:92029">Dartagnan</a>, <a href="/user/uid:308949">Phoebe Loosinhouse</a>, <a href="/user/uid:100108">jello5929</a>, <a href="/user/uid:327009">goodpractice</a>, <a href="/user/uid:62088">the fan man</a>, <a href="/user/uid:115624">Thomas Twinnings</a>, <a href="/user/uid:2823">Chi</a>, <a href="/user/uid:96369">Matt Z</a>, <a href="/user/uid:62669">tallen387</a>, <a href="/user/uid:39858">Hillbilly Dem</a>, <a href="/user/uid:3037">Phoenix Woman</a>, <a href="/user/uid:46465">NoMoreLies</a>, <a href="/user/uid:947717">travelerxxx</a>, <a href="/user/uid:100167">Midwesterners</a>, <a href="/user/uid:51000">schumann</a>, <a href="/user/uid:75329">JVolvo</a>, <a href="/user/uid:14168">movie buff</a>, <a href="/user/uid:125975">Metro99</a>, <a href="/user/uid:116838">elwior</a>, <a href="/user/uid:1130446">WI Lurker</a>
    </dd>
  
</dl></div>

  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>"We're going to your lower taxes". Translation: We're going to implement a flat tax with monster tax cuts for the wealthy, and maybe a bone for you.</p>
<p>"We're going to increase your take home pay!" Translation: We're going to reduce your SS and Medicare contributions so that we can create crisis with these two programs and eliminate them.</p>
<p>"We're going to get government out of education." Translation, there will be no Federal dollars supporting education goals.</p>
<p>"We're going to remove the heavy hand of regulation." Translation: We'll let industry foul the air and water you use. Then when you get sick, you're on your own. Why?.....</p>
<p>"We'll institute tort reform to get lawyers out of your life". Translation: We'll make it practically impossible for you to sue a corporation.</p>

  </div>
  <div class="cf">
  
  <p class="sig">
"Liberty" is a living wage. "Freedom" is not worrying about your medical bills.
</p>
  <p class="cb">by <a href="/user/uid:132234">billybam</a> on <a href="/comments/1363137/55613244#c34">Sun Feb 08, 2015 at 11:32:02 AM PST</a></p>
