<li id="c359">

  <div class="cx" id="cx55627121">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">Gore was trailing in the 98 polls</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1363137/55627121#c359?mode=alone;showrate=1#c359">0+ / 0-</a>)</span>
  </h5>

  
  


  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>so how was it his election to lose? That doesn't make sense. It was widely assumed that Bush was the GOP front runner. Sure he had opponents, but he was clearly the man to beat and no one did.</p>

  </div>
  <div class="cf">
  
  <p class="sig"></p>
  <p class="cb">by <a href="/user/uid:304786">Dr Swig Mcjigger</a> on <a href="/comments/1363137/55627121#c359">Tue Feb 10, 2015 at 07:37:21 AM PST</a></p>
  <p class="cl">
  
 
 
  [ <a href="#c358">Parent</a> ] 
    
   

 
 
 </p> 
  </div>
  </div>
