<p>Pundit in me says that Clinton will not be running a Clinton-esque campaign, she will be running an Obama-esque campaign, judging by her hires. I suspect this means she will call Jeb out on his shit, and ask him to say what he would recommend to address income inequality. Because he won't have anything.</p>

