<div class="crs"><dl>
  <dt>Recommended by:</dt><dd>
  <a href="/user/uid:3037">Phoenix Woman</a>, <a href="/user/uid:51716">caliberal2001</a>, <a href="/user/uid:1130446">WI Lurker</a>
    </dd>
  
</dl></div>

  

  <div class="ct">
  <p>I wish people would stop laying on the "candidate of inevitability crap. She knows it cost her last time, she's got a lot of Obama's team, she currently doesn't HAVE a campaign strategy because she is technically NOT campaigning (FEC wise), and for some reason people are ripping her about it in Feb, 20 months before the election. We simply don't know her campaign strategy, that's the be all, end all. Hearteningly, the Obama people are much better at winning elections then the DCCC. It's good she has them on her team.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="cf">
  
  <p class="sig"></p>
  <p class="cb">by <a href="/user/uid:1056281">PCalith</a> on <a href="/comments/1363137/55615098#c163">Sun Feb 08, 2015 at 03:34:16 PM PST</a></p>
