<li id="c249">

  <div class="cx" id="cx55616321">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">might such a tax be ruled unconstitutional?</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1363137/55616321#c249?mode=alone;showrate=1#c249">1+ / 0-</a>)</span>
