<li id="c342">

  <div class="cx" id="cx55621704">
   <h5> <a class="de">&nbsp;</a><span class="cu">Outflanked?</span>


<span class="crd ntb">(<a href="/comments/1363137/55621704#c342?mode=alone;showrate=1#c342">0+ / 0-</a>)</span>
  </h5>

  
  


  

  <div class="ct">
  
<p>If she continues to cling to her husband's "Republican lite" economic and fiscal policies, you better believe she'll be outflanked! &nbsp;She has to decide, is she a Democrat or not?</p>

  </div>
  <div class="cf">
  
  <p class="sig">
"The test of our progress is not whether we add to the abundance of those who have much. It is whether we provide enough to those who have little. " --Franklin D. Roosevelt
</p>
  <p class="cb">by <a href="/user/uid:317200">jg6544</a> on <a href="/comments/1363137/55621704#c342">Mon Feb 09, 2015 at 12:54:42 PM PST</a></p>
  <p class="cl">
  
 
 
  
    
   

 
 
 </p> 
  </div>
